<br>
Think of it like this<br>
<br>
<br>
1 to 900    (1 being level 51 start and 900 being level 60 max)<br>
<br>
Atm lets say you have  850 exp points so your level 60 and fairly well in.<br>
<br>
How however you split these 900 exp points between 10....maybe giving 120 for  level 54 and only 80 for level etc....you still need 900 exp points to max (basically how it is atm)....so you would need in this example 50 more exp points to max your exp.<br>
<br>
What their planning on doing is making it so 100 = 1 level for example.  So it will STILL need 50 more exp points to max your level 60.<br>
<br>
Infact ....in theory if they are including level 60 ...people who are level 59 will ding to levelk 60 eairly because level 60 needs far less exp to raise and lower...and the people in 60 will look like they have gained exp (not really though).<br>
